// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1813 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: dba36030-48f5-543e-b7be-03d65c1734b0

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*")
